_comment: _注释（这里只是界面引导，战斗内引导另外配置）
stage: 所属阶段(-1:完成新手战斗，-2:主城点15下跳过引导)
specialName: 名称(特殊非正常引导触发)
startSceen: 打开该场景/界面时触发，默认主城触发（all为对应战斗胜利，升级，主城等界面触发）
order: 排序（多个stage满足，小的越先触发）
service: 服务器交互(1、记录引导；3、进关卡记录引导，战斗返回继续引导)
awardChoose: 默默塞和初始选择卡牌相关的奖励
gotoScene: 1主城2关卡界面(每条引导最后触发)
gotoStep: 跳转步骤（该stage的最后一条配置生效）
showType: 表现样式（1、引导员，2剧情对话，3、空白）
force: 角色位置在 1左 2右（通用设置）
useRoleFigure: 使用角色形象配置<id;字段> id 0 为主角形象（样式2）
offPos: 对话角色额外偏移位置（样式2）
headRes: 头像资源（样式1，特殊用于样式2）
headPos: 头像额外偏移位置，初始为工程位置（样式1）
roleName: 角色名称（样式1，特殊用于样式2）
roleName_tw: 角色名称（样式1，特殊用于样式2）
roleName_en: 角色名称（样式1，特殊用于样式2）
roleName_kr: 角色名称（样式1，特殊用于样式2）_韩
talkContent: 聊天内容（富文本配置）（通用设置）
talkContent_tw: 聊天内容（富文本配置）（通用设置）
talkContent_en: 聊天内容（富文本配置）（通用设置）
talkContent_vn: 聊天内容（富文本配置）（通用设置）_越南
talkContent_kr: 聊天内容（富文本配置）（通用设置）_韩
__tagName: 要点击的控件名称（样式1）
tagName: 要点击的控件名称（样式1）
jumpToNode: 跳到目标节点（需要程序逻辑增加）
animatePos: 动画额外偏移位置（样式1）

talkContent: Hello there
talkContent_tw: 你好
talkContent_en: Hello there
talkContent_kr: 반갑구나!

talkContent: Hello, new trainer, welcome to this magical world.
talkContent_tw: 你好啊，新來的訓練家，歡迎來到這個神奇的世界。
talkContent_en: Hello, new trainer, welcome to this magical world.
talkContent_kr: "신참 트레이너, 포켓몬의 세계에 온 것을 환영한다!"

talkContent: People here like to call me Professor Oak. I'll be guiding you into this magical world.
talkContent_tw: 這裡的人們喜歡叫我大木博士，我負責指引你進入這個神奇的世界。
talkContent_en: People here like to call me Professor Oak. I'll be guiding you into this magical world.
talkContent_kr: 이곳 사람들은 날 오박사라고 부르지. 난 너를 이 신비한 세계로 안내하는 일을 맡을 거란다.

talkContent: By the way, please tell me your name. I still don't know your name yet, since you've just arrived.
talkContent_tw: 對了，你剛來，我還不知道你叫啥呢，告訴我下你的名字吧。
talkContent_en: By the way, please tell me your name. I still don't know your name yet, since you've just arrived.
talkContent_kr: "참, 그러고 보니 아직 네 이름도 듣지 못했구나."

talkContent: Sounds like a good name, I seem to be able to see your future as a Pokémon master!
talkContent_tw: 聽起來是個不錯的名字呢，我在你身上仿佛看到了你成為神奇寶貝大師的未來呢。
talkContent_en: Sounds like a good name, I seem to be able to see your future as a Pokémon master!
talkContent_kr: 좋은 이름이로구나. 왠지 네가 장차 포켓몬 마스터가 될 수 있을 것 같다는 느낌이 드는걸.

talkContent: I'll keep trying my best!
talkContent_tw: 我會一直努力的！
talkContent_en: I'll keep trying my best!
talkContent_kr: 최선을 다할게요!

talkContent: Well, well, well. I hope you can become a master of the generation through fighting and catching Pokémons.
talkContent_tw: 嗯，很好，很好，希望你能夠通過對戰、收服，成為一代大師呢。
talkContent_en: Well, well, well. I hope you can become a master of the generation through fighting and catching Pokémons.
talkContent_kr: "그래, 아주 좋아. 부디 다양한 대결과 포획을 통해 뛰어난 트레이너가 될 수 있길 바란다."

talkContent: But, since we are going on a journey, I'll have to give you a new companion first, otherwise nothing can be started.
talkContent_tw: 不過，既然要踏上旅途，我得先給你一個新的夥伴，不然什麼都沒法開始啊。
talkContent_en: But, since we are going on a journey, I'll have to give you a new companion first, otherwise nothing can be started.
talkContent_kr: 하지만 여정에 오르기 위해서는 새로운 동료가 필요하지. 그렇지 않으면 아무것도 시작할 수 없을 거야.

talkContent: Which is the Pokémon of your choice?
talkContent_tw: 你有心儀的精靈麼？
talkContent_en: Which is the Pokémon of your choice?
talkContent_kr: 마음에 드는 포켓몬이 있니?

talkContent: I'm not too sure of that...
talkContent_tw: 不太清楚呢
talkContent_en: I'm not too sure of that...
talkContent_kr: 잘 모르겠어요

talkContent: Well, since you don't have any idea yet, come here and take a closer look at them. Choose carefully, as there is no turning back.
talkContent_tw: 嘛，既然還沒想法，那就這邊來，仔細看看他們，你一定要認真選擇哦，這兒可沒後悔藥。
talkContent_en: Well, since you don't have any idea yet, come here and take a closer look at them. Choose carefully, as there is no turning back.
talkContent_kr: "뭐, 그럼 이쪽으로 와서 자세히 살펴 보거라. 신중하게 선택하는 게 좋아. 다시 바꿀 수 없으니 말이야."

talkContent: Alright, enjoy your new adventure!
talkContent_tw: 那麼，請盡情開始冒險吧
talkContent_en: Alright, enjoy your new adventure!
talkContent_kr: 그럼 모험을 시작하거라.

talkContent: I'm looking to see you becoming the next Pokémon Master!
talkContent_tw: 我期待你能成為新的神奇寶貝大師哦
talkContent_en: I'm looking to see you becoming the next Pokémon Master!
talkContent_kr: 네가 새로운 포켓몬 마스터가 되는 날을 기대하고 있으마.

talkContent: Wait, I forgot to tell you something.
talkContent_tw: 等等，還有個事情忘記交代給你了
talkContent_en: Wait, I forgot to tell you something.
talkContent_kr: "아, 잠깐, 중요한 일을 하나 잊었구나."

talkContent: I have another Pokémon for you. although he can be a little feisty at times, I believe he will also grow into a good companion in your adventure.
talkContent_tw: 這還有一隻精靈要交給你，雖然他偶爾脾氣有點暴躁，但是我相信他也會成長為你冒險旅途中的好夥伴
talkContent_en: I have another Pokémon for you. although he can be a little feisty at times, I believe he will also grow into a good companion in your adventure.
talkContent_kr: "이 포켓몬도 네게 부탁하마. 가끔 성격이 거칠어지긴 하지만, 네 좋은 동료가 되어줄 거라고 믿는다."

talkContent: Pika! Pika!
talkContent_tw: 皮卡！皮卡！
talkContent_en: Pika! Pika!
talkContent_kr: 피카! 피카!

talkContent: Pikachu, let's fight together!
talkContent_tw: 皮卡丘，那就讓我們一起並肩作戰吧！
talkContent_en: Pikachu, let's fight together!
talkContent_kr: "피카츄, 그럼 이제 함께 힘을 합쳐 싸우자!"

talkContent: Next, let's familiarize and understand this magical Pokémon World with the Rotom Pokédex.
talkContent_tw: 接下來，就讓圖鑒洛托姆來幫助你熟悉和瞭解這個神奇的精靈世界吧
talkContent_en: Next, let's familiarize and understand this magical Pokémon World with the Rotom Pokédex.
talkContent_kr: 이제부터 로토무 도감이 널 도와서 이 신비한 포켓몬의 세계를 안내해줄 거다.

talkContent: Evolution is a phenomenon that happens in the Pokémon world. Some Pokémons, under certain conditions, will evolve into another Pokémon during that growing process. Evolution is not merely a physical transformation but a change in base stats, moves, and some undergo a change in type.
talkContent_tw: 進化是精靈寶可夢世界之中的一種現象。有些精靈在成長過程中，在特定的條件下，會進化成為另一種精靈。進化不僅僅是身體上的變化，進化後的精靈有不同的種族值，學會不同的招式，有的甚至還會改變屬性。
talkContent_en: Evolution is a phenomenon that happens in the Pokémon world. Some Pokémons, under certain conditions, will evolve into another Pokémon during that growing process. Evolution is not merely a physical transformation but a change in base stats, moves, and some undergo a change in type.
talkContent_kr: "진화는 포켓몬 세계에 존재하는 현상 중 하나야 로토. 어떤 정령들은 성장하면서 특정 조건을 달성하면 다른 종의 포켓몬으로 진화하게 돼 로토. 포켓몬이 진화하면 몸도 강해지지만, 기존과는 다른 종족값을 얻거나, 새로운 기술을 배우고, 심지어는 타입까지 달라질 수도 있어 로토."

talkContent_tw: 每天完成日常任務，可以快速提升等級，不要忘記了喲
talkContent_en: Don't forget to complete daily quests daily to increase level quickly.
talkContent_kr: 매일 일일 퀘스트를 완료하면 빠르게 레벨을 높일 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: Congratulations! You got the "Adventure Pass", let's see what it can do!
talkContent_tw: 恭喜你，獲得了“冒險執照”，讓我們去看一看有什麼作用吧！
talkContent_en: Congratulations! You got the "Adventure Pass", let's see what it can do!
talkContent_kr: "축하해, “모험 허가증”을 획득했어 로토, 어서 확인해 보자 로토!"

talkContent: Tap "Training" to open the training list.
talkContent_tw: 在這裡點擊“養成”，打開養成列表
talkContent_en: Tap "Training" to open the training list.
talkContent_kr: 육성을 터치해서 육성 메뉴를 열어 봐 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to open the Adventure Pass interface.
talkContent_tw: 點一下這裡，打開冒險執照介面
talkContent_en: Tap here to open the Adventure Pass interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해서 모험 허가증 메뉴를 열어 봐 로토.

talkContent: Moves can be upgraded to gain extra privileges, while upgraded materials can be obtained through completing daily quests.
talkContent_tw: 可以提升技能來獲得額外特權，升級材料可以通過日常任務獲得
talkContent_en: Moves can be upgraded to gain extra privileges, while upgraded materials can be obtained through completing daily quests.
talkContent_kr: 기술을 향상시켜서 추가 특권을 얻을 수 있어 로토. 레벨업 재료는 일일 퀘스트에서 획득하면 돼 로토.

talkContent: Upgrading moves can give you more EXP, which can then be used to increase your Privilege level.
talkContent_tw: 提升技能可以獲得經驗，經驗積累滿了可以提升特權等級
talkContent_en: Upgrading moves can give you more EXP, which can then be used to increase your Privilege level.
talkContent_kr: "기술을 향상시키면 경험치를 얻을 수 있고, 경험치가 쌓이면 특권 레벨이 높아질 거야 로토."

talkContent: New feature#C0xE77421#[Arena]#C0x5B545B#  is now open!
talkContent_tw: 新的功能#C0xE77421#【競技場】#C0x5B545B#開啟了哦
talkContent_en: New feature#C0xE77421#[Arena]#C0x5B545B#  is now open!
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#[아레나]#C0x5B545B# 기능이 개방됐어 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the Arena selection interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入競技的選擇介面
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Arena selection interface.
talkContent_kr: 터치해 아레나 선택 메뉴로 들어가 봐 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the Arena.
talkContent_tw: 從這裡可以點擊進入競技場
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Arena.
talkContent_kr: 아레나는 여기로 입장할 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: Welcome to the Arena!
talkContent_tw: 你好，歡迎來到競技場
talkContent_en: Welcome to the Arena!
talkContent_kr: 아레나에 오신 것을 환영합니다.

talkContent: Challenge players in the arena to improve your rankings.
talkContent_tw: 在競技場中可以挑戰玩家提升排名
talkContent_en: Challenge players in the arena to improve your rankings.
talkContent_kr: 아레나에서는 다른 유저에게 도전해 순위를 높일 수 있답니다.

talkContent: This is the rank rewards page. You can check for your rank and claim rewards here if there's any changes.
talkContent_tw: 這裡可以排名獎勵頁面，排名變更後可以在這裡檢視和領取獎勵
talkContent_en: This is the rank rewards page. You can check for your rank and claim rewards here if there's any changes.
talkContent_kr: 이쪽은 순위 보상 페이지입니다. 순위가 변경되면 이곳에서 조회하고 보상을 수령할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Point rewards can be viewed here. Points will be given regardless of victory or defeat, and rewards will be given after earning a certain number of points.
talkContent_tw: 這裡可以檢視積分獎勵，挑戰無論勝負，均可以獲得積分，積分到達一定數量後可以獲得獎勵
talkContent_en: Point rewards can be viewed here. Points will be given regardless of victory or defeat, and rewards will be given after earning a certain number of points.
talkContent_kr: "이쪽에서는 포인트 보상을 확인할 수 있어요. 도전 시 승부에 관계 없이 포인트를 획득하며, 포인트가 일정 수치에 도달하면 보상을 받을 수 있어요."

talkContent: You can also tap here to switch the display image in the arena.
talkContent_tw: 你也可以點擊這裡切換在競技場中的展示形象
talkContent_en: You can also tap here to switch the display image in the arena.
talkContent_kr: 또한 여기에서 아레나의 표시 설정을 전환할 수 있어요.

talkContent: You can set up your defensive lineup here.
talkContent_tw: 這裡可以設置你的防守陣容
talkContent_en: You can set up your defensive lineup here.
talkContent_kr: 여기에서 방어 라인업을 설정하세요.

talkContent: So, let's start the battle of honor!
talkContent_tw: 那麼，開始屬於你榮耀的戰鬥吧！
talkContent_en: So, let's start the battle of honor!
talkContent_kr: 그럼 영광을 위한 대결을 시작하세요!

talkContent: Tap here before the challenge to check the details of your opponents, just in case.
talkContent_tw: 挑戰之前可以點擊這裡可以檢視對手的詳細資訊，有備無患
talkContent_en: Tap here before the challenge to check the details of your opponents, just in case.
talkContent_kr: 도전하기 전 이곳에서 상대의 정보를 확인할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Good luck then!
talkContent_tw: 那麼，祝你好運了！
talkContent_en: Good luck then!
talkContent_kr: 그럼 행운을 빌게요!

talkContent: New feature#C0xE77421#Daily Dungeon #C0x5B545B#  is now open!
talkContent_tw: 新的功能#C0xE77421#日常副本#C0x5B545B#開啟了哦
talkContent_en: New feature#C0xE77421#Daily Dungeon #C0x5B545B#  is now open!
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#일일 던전#C0x5B545B# 기능이 개방됐어 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the Adventure selection interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入冒險的選擇介面
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Adventure selection interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 모험 선택 메뉴로 들어가 봐 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the Daily Dungeon.
talkContent_tw: 從這裡可以點擊進入日常副本
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Daily Dungeon.
talkContent_kr: 일일 던전은 여기로 입장할 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter Coin Dungeon.
talkContent_tw: 點此進入金幣副本
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter Coin Dungeon.
talkContent_kr: 코인 던전에 입장해 봐 로토.

talkContent: You can fight the monsters and lots of coins here.
talkContent_tw: 這裡可以挑戰怪物獲得大量的金幣
talkContent_en: You can fight the monsters and lots of coins here.
talkContent_kr: 도전을 통해 대량의 코인를 획득할 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: The higher the damage dealt to the enemy, the more rewards you get.
talkContent_tw: 對敵人造成的傷害越高，獲得的獎勵也就越多
talkContent_en: The higher the damage dealt to the enemy, the more rewards you get.
talkContent_kr: 적에게 입히는 피해가 클수록 획득하는 보상이 증가할 거야 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to start preparing for the battle.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入開始為戰鬥進行準備
talkContent_en: Tap here to start preparing for the battle.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 전투 준비를 시작하자 로토.

talkContent: When you are ready, let's fight!
talkContent_tw: 準備好以後就開始戰鬥吧
talkContent_en: When you are ready, let's fight!
talkContent_kr: 준비가 끝났다면 전투를 시작하자 로토.

talkContent: New feature#C0xE77421#[union]#C0x5B545B#  is now open!
talkContent_tw: 新的功能#C0xE77421#【公會】#C0x5B545B#開啟了哦
talkContent_en: New feature#C0xE77421#[union]#C0x5B545B#  is now open!
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#[길드]#C0x5B545B# 기능이 개방됐어 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to open the unions list.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡可以打開公會列表
talkContent_en: Tap here to open the unions list.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치하면 길드 목록을 열 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: You can find some unions to join here, one trainer can only send up to 3 union requests at once.
talkContent_tw: 你可以在這裡找到一些公會加入，一個人能同時最多申請3個公會哦
talkContent_en: You can find some unions to join here, one trainer can only send up to 3 union requests at once.
talkContent_kr: "여기서 길드를 찾아서 가입할 수 있고, 신청은 동시에 3개 길드까지 보낼 수 있어 로토."

talkContent: If you want to find yourself a home quickly, you can tap [Quick Join] to instantly join a union that meets the requirement.
talkContent_tw: 如果想快速找到一個家，你可以點擊【快速加入】直接加入一個符合條件的公會
talkContent_en: If you want to find yourself a home quickly, you can tap [Quick Join] to instantly join a union that meets the requirement.
talkContent_kr: "빠르게 길드를 찾고 싶다면, [빠른 가입]을 터치해 조건에 맞는 길드에 바로 가입할 수 있어 로토."

talkContent: If you've not joined a union or have not found a union of your choice, you may tap [Create union] to build your own union.
talkContent_tw: 如果現在還沒有公會，或者沒有你想加入的公會，你可以點擊【創建公會】自己來創建一個
talkContent_en: If you've not joined a union or have not found a union of your choice, you may tap [Create union] to build your own union.
talkContent_kr: "아직 가입할 수 있는 길드가 없거나 마음에 드는 길드가 없다면, [길드 창설]을 눌러 직접 만들어도 돼 로토."

talkContent: Welcome to the union interface. Here is the place where you can grow and develop with like-minded companions!
talkContent_tw: 歡迎你進入公會介面，在這裡，你可以和志同道合的朋友一起發展壯大哦
talkContent_en: Welcome to the union interface. Here is the place where you can grow and develop with like-minded companions!
talkContent_kr: 여긴 길드 메뉴야 로토. 여기서는 마음이 맞는 친구들과 함께 성장할 수 있어 로토.

_comment: Here is the daily guild to-do information
talkContent: Here are the information of the union's daily to-dos.
talkContent_tw: 這裡有每天的公會待辦資訊
talkContent_en: Here are the information of the union's daily to-dos.
talkContent_kr: 여기에는 매일 길드의 정보가 표시돼 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter [Donation Center]
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡，進入【捐贈中心】
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter [Donation Center]
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 [기부센터]로 입장해 로토.

talkContent: You can check union Quests here.
talkContent_tw: 這裡可以檢視公會任務
talkContent_en: You can check union Quests here.
talkContent_kr: 여기서는 길드 퀘스트를 확인할 수 있어 로토.

_comment: Click here to go to the donation page
talkContent: Tap here to enter the donation interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡，進入捐獻頁面
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the donation interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 기부 메뉴로 입장해 로토.

_comment: You can choose to spend a small amount of gold coins or diamonds to contribute to the guild, and at the same time get guild experience and guild coins in return
talkContent: You can choose to spend a small amount of coins or diamonds to upgrade the union building, while gaining union EXP and union coin in return.
talkContent_tw: 你可以選擇消費少量的金幣或鑽石為公會添磚加瓦，同時獲得公會經驗和公會幣回報
talkContent_en: You can choose to spend a small amount of coins or diamonds to upgrade the union building, while gaining union EXP and union coin in return.
talkContent_kr: "소량의 코인이나 다이아를 소모해서·길드 발전을 위해 기부할 수 있어 로토, 그리고 길드 경험치와 길드 코인을 얻을 수 있어 로토."

_comment: Click here to enter the bonus page
talkContent: Tap here to enter the Red Packet interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入紅包頁面
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Red Packet interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 보너스 메뉴로 입장해 로토.

_comment: There are red envelopes that the guild can receive every day, but the number is limited, so be quick!
talkContent: There are Red Packets to be collected in the union every day, but as the quantity is limited, fastest fingers get it first.
talkContent_tw: 這裡有每天公會可以領取的紅包，不過數量有限，手快有手慢無哦
talkContent_en: There are Red Packets to be collected in the union every day, but as the quantity is limited, fastest fingers get it first.
talkContent_kr: 매일 길드에서 보너스를 수령할 수 있어 로토. 하지만 수량이 정해져 있으니까 서둘러야 해 로토.

_comment: Participate in the construction of the guild. After the guild is upgraded, the weight and quantity of red envelopes can be increased.
talkContent: Participate in the construction of the union and increase the weight and quantity of Red Packets after the union is levels up.
talkContent_tw: 參與公會建設，公會升級後可以增加紅包的重量和數量哦
talkContent_en: Participate in the construction of the union and increase the weight and quantity of Red Packets after the union is levels up.
talkContent_kr: 길드 건설에 참가하면 길드 레벨업 시 보너스의 중량과 수량을 늘릴 수 있어 로토.

_comment: Here are red envelopes sent by guild leaders. If you see red envelopes here, don’t hesitate to start!
talkContent: Tap here to check the Red Packets given by your comrades.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡可以檢視戰友們發放的紅包
talkContent_en: Tap here to check the Red Packets given by your comrades.
talkContent_kr: 이곳을 터치하면 동료들이 보낸 보너스를 확인할 수 있어 로토.

_comment: Here are the red envelopes you can send. Sending red envelopes does not require any resources
talkContent: There are Red Packets for you to distribute here, it is free!
talkContent_tw: 這裡有你可以發放的紅包，發紅包不花錢哦
talkContent_en: There are Red Packets for you to distribute here, it is free!
talkContent_kr: 여기에는 네가 보낸 보너스를 확인할 수 있어. 보너스를 보내는 건 무료야 로토.

_comment: If you don't have any red envelopes yet, you can click here to see how to get them
talkContent: If you do not have any Red Packet to distribute, tap here to see how you can get a Red Packet.
talkContent_tw: 如果你還沒有可發放的紅包，你可以點擊這裡，檢視如何獲取紅包
talkContent_en: If you do not have any Red Packet to distribute, tap here to see how you can get a Red Packet.
talkContent_kr: "아직 보낼 수 있는 보너스가 없다면, 여길 터치해서 어떻게 보너스를 획득하는지 확인해 봐 로토."

talkContent: Dear trainer, the Adventure Road is open. You may now challenge it!
talkContent_tw: 親愛的訓練師，冒險之路已開啟，可進行前往挑戰！
talkContent_en: Dear trainer, the Adventure Road is open. You may now challenge it!
talkContent_kr: "트레이너님, 모험의 길이 개방됐어요. 이제 도전을 시작해 보세요!"

talkContent: Tap here to enter the "Adventure"
talkContent_tw: 請點擊這裡，進入“冒險”
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the "Adventure"
talkContent_kr: 모험에 진입하세요.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the "Adventure Road"
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡，進入“冒險之路”
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the "Adventure Road"
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 “모험의 길”로 입장하세요.

talkContent: Levels to be challenged are shown here.
talkContent_tw: 這裡顯示可挑戰的關卡
talkContent_en: Levels to be challenged are shown here.
talkContent_kr: 이곳에서는 도전할 수 있는 스테이지가 나타납니다.

talkContent: You get a chance to reset the level once a day, it will restore to the initial level status after the reset.
talkContent_tw: 每日有一次重置關卡機會，重置後初始關卡狀態
talkContent_en: You get a chance to reset the level once a day, it will restore to the initial level status after the reset.
talkContent_kr: "매일 스테이지 초기화 기회가 한 번 주어지며, 초기화 시 스테이지의 상태가 초기 상태로 돌아가요."

talkContent: After the level is initialized, trainers can use one-tap blitz to reach the highest level to be challenged currently.
talkContent_tw: 關卡初始化後，可使用一鍵掃蕩通關至當前可挑戰的最大關卡
talkContent_en: After the level is initialized, trainers can use one-tap blitz to reach the highest level to be challenged currently.
talkContent_kr: "스테이지를 초기화한 후, 간편소탕을 사용해 현재 도전 가능한 최고 스테이지까지 클리어할 수 있어요."

talkContent: Tap the first level!
talkContent_tw: 現在讓我們點擊第一關吧！
talkContent_en: Tap the first level!
talkContent_kr: 이제 첫 스테이지를 터치해 보세요!

talkContent: Trinket Card can give Star Up items to greatly boost the types of the trinkets.
talkContent_tw: 飾品抽卡能夠獲取升星道具，可以大幅度提升飾品屬性
talkContent_en: Trinket Card can give Star Up items to greatly boost the types of the trinkets.
talkContent_kr: 액세서리 뽑기를 통해 승급 아이템을 획득하면 액세서리의 속성을 대폭 증가시킬 수 있어요.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the Card Draw interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡，進入抽卡介面。
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Card Draw interface.
talkContent_kr: 뽑기 메뉴로 들어가 봐 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to join the Trinket Draw.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡打開飾品抽卡
talkContent_en: Tap here to join the Trinket Draw.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해서 액세서리 뽑기를 열어 보세요.

talkContent: Don't forget that you can draw the trinket card for free once every day!
talkContent_tw: 飾品抽卡每天都可以免費抽取一次，千萬不要忘記哦!
talkContent_en: Don't forget that you can draw the trinket card for free once every day!
talkContent_kr: 액세서리 뽑기는 매일 무료로 한 번 진행할 수 있으니 잊지 마세요!

_comment: Accessory draw card - open the box

talkContent: There are all sorts of Pokémons in this magical world. Don't you want to catch more of them?
talkContent_tw: 在這個神奇的世界裡，存在著各種各樣的精靈，你想不想擁有更多的精靈呢？
talkContent_en: There are all sorts of Pokémons in this magical world. Don't you want to catch more of them?
talkContent_kr: 이 신비한 세계에서는 다양한 포켓몬이 존재한다 로토. 더 많은 포켓몬을 얻고 싶지 않아 로토?

talkContent: Let's try drawing some cards and summon new Pokémons!
talkContent_tw: 讓我們去試試抽卡召喚新的精靈吧！
talkContent_en: Let's try drawing some cards and summon new Pokémons!
talkContent_kr: 그럼 포켓몬 뽑기로 새로운 포켓몬을 소환해 보자 로토!

talkContent: Tap here to enter the Card Draw interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡，進入抽卡介面。
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the Card Draw interface.
talkContent_kr: 뽑기 메뉴로 들어가 봐 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to draw a card!
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡開始抽卡吧！
talkContent_en: Tap here to draw a card!
talkContent_kr: 터치해서 뽑기를 시작해봐 로토!

talkContent: Congratulations on getting a new Pokémon, let's add it to the line-up!
talkContent_tw: 恭喜你獲得了新精靈，讓我們把它加入陣容吧！
talkContent_en: Congratulations on getting a new Pokémon, let's add it to the line-up!
talkContent_kr: "축하해, 새로운 포켓몬을 획득했어 로토. 그럼 어서 라인업에 추가해 보자 로토!"

_comment: Main city layout - return to the main interface
talkContent: #C0xE77421#Tap#C0x5B545B# here to return to the main interface.
talkContent_tw: #C0xE77421#點擊#C0x5B545B#這裡，返回主介面
talkContent_en: #C0xE77421#Tap#C0x5B545B# here to return to the main interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 #C0xE77421#터치#C0x5B545B#해 메인화면으로 돌아가 로토.

talkContent: Congratulations, you have successfully activated the talent feature. Let's go and check it out.
talkContent_tw: 恭喜你，成功開啟了天賦系統，讓我們去看一看吧
talkContent_en: Congratulations, you have successfully activated the talent feature. Let's go and check it out.
talkContent_kr: 축하드려요. 특성 시스템이 개방됐어요. 그럼 어서 살펴볼까요?

talkContent: Congratulations, you have successfully activated the talent feature. Tap "Training".
talkContent_tw: 恭喜你，成功開啟了天賦系統，點擊“養成”
talkContent_en: Congratulations, you have successfully activated the talent feature. Tap "Training".
talkContent_kr: 축하드려요. 특성 시스템이 개방됐어요. “육성”을 터치해 보세요.

talkContent: Tap "Talent" to enter the control panel.
talkContent_tw: 點擊“天賦”進入功能面板
talkContent_en: Tap "Talent" to enter the control panel.
talkContent_kr: 터치해 “특성” 메뉴로 진입하세요.

talkContent: Talent points can be obtained in adventures. It can increase talent levels and increase combat capabilities.
talkContent_tw: 冒險中可以獲得天賦點，天賦點提升天賦等級，增加戰鬥能力
talkContent_en: Talent points can be obtained in adventures. It can increase talent levels and increase combat capabilities.
talkContent_kr: "모험 중에는 특성포인트를 획득할 수 있어요. 특성포인트는 특성의 레벨을 높여, 전투 능력을 증가시킬 수 있죠."

talkContent: Tap here to view the Talent Moves.
talkContent_tw: 點一下這裡，可以打開天賦技能
talkContent_en: Tap here to view the Talent Moves.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해서 특성 기술을 열어 보세요.

talkContent: Congratulations trainer, you can now dispatch Pokémons on a quest!
talkContent_tw: 恭喜訓練師，你現在可以委派精靈去做任務啦！
talkContent_en: Congratulations trainer, you can now dispatch Pokémons on a quest!
talkContent_kr: "축하드려요, 트레이너님, 이제 포켓몬을 파견해 퀘스트를 진행할 수 있어요!"

talkContent: Tap to enter "Adventure"
talkContent_tw: 點擊進入“冒險”
talkContent_en: Tap to enter "Adventure"
talkContent_kr: 모험에 진입하세요.

talkContent: Tap to select "Dispatch"
talkContent_tw: 點擊選擇“派遣”
talkContent_en: Tap to select "Dispatch"
talkContent_kr: 파견을 선택하세요.

talkContent: The trainer can assign various quests to the Pokémons, where they will be rewarded upon completion of the quests.
talkContent_tw: 訓練師可委派精靈接取各種任務，任務完成可獲得相應獎勵
talkContent_en: The trainer can assign various quests to the Pokémons, where they will be rewarded upon completion of the quests.
talkContent_kr: "트레이너님은 포켓몬을 파견해 각종 퀘스트를 진행할 수 있고, 퀘스트를 완료하면 해당하는 보상을 획득할 수 있어요."

talkContent: All quests are given a grade. The higher the grade, the better the reward.
talkContent_tw: 每個任務有對應的品質，品質越高獎勵越好。
talkContent_en: All quests are given a grade. The higher the grade, the better the reward.
talkContent_kr: 각 퀘스트의 등급에 따라 보상이 증가한답니다.

talkContent: The corresponding quest information and rewards are displayed on the quest interface.
talkContent_tw: 任務面板上顯示對應的任務資訊和獎勵
talkContent_en: The corresponding quest information and rewards are displayed on the quest interface.
talkContent_kr: 퀘스트 화면에서는 해당 퀘스트의 정보와 보상을 확인할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Tap to select quest and begin dispatching your Pokémons.
talkContent_tw: 點擊選擇任務，開始進行任務派遣吧。
talkContent_en: Tap to select quest and begin dispatching your Pokémons.
talkContent_kr: 퀘스트를 선택하고 퀘스트 파견을 시작하세요.

talkContent: Dear trainer, you have successfully activated the explorer device feature, let's check it out!
talkContent_tw: 親愛的訓練家，你已成功開啟探險器的玩法，讓我們來看一下吧！
talkContent_en: Dear trainer, you have successfully activated the explorer device feature, let's check it out!
talkContent_kr: "트레이너님, 탐지기 시스템이 개방됐어요. 어서 같이 살펴보아요!"

talkContent: Tap here to open the "Training" interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡打開“養成”
talkContent_en: Tap here to open the "Training" interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해서 “육성”을 열어 보세요.

talkContent: Tap here to open the "Training" interface.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡打開“養成”
talkContent_en: Tap here to open the "Training" interface.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해서 “육성”을 열어 보세요.

talkContent: Trainers can get the Explorer Device component to activate and upgrade the Explorer Device. Let's go for a treasure hunt to get a component!
talkContent_tw: 訓練師可通過獲得探險器元件來啟動和進階探險器。讓我們來尋寶一次來獲得元件吧！
talkContent_en: Trainers can get the Explorer Device component to activate and upgrade the Explorer Device. Let's go for a treasure hunt to get a component!
talkContent_kr: 트레이너님은 탐지기 부품을 획득해 탐지기를 활성화하고 진급시킬 수 있어요. 그럼 보물찾기를 통해 부품을 획득해 볼까요?

talkContent: Tap here to enter "Treasure Hunt"
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入“尋寶”
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter "Treasure Hunt"
talkContent_kr: 보물찾기로 입장하세요.

talkContent: Tap here to conduct "free treasure hunt" 1 time.
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進行“免費尋寶”一次
talkContent_en: Tap here to conduct "free treasure hunt" 1 time.
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 “무료 보물찾기”를 진행하세요.

talkContent: Tap here to activate and upgrade the correspond component.
talkContent_tw: 點擊對應元件可進行元件的啟動和升級
talkContent_en: Tap here to activate and upgrade the correspond component.
talkContent_kr: 해당 부품을 터치하면 부품의 활성화 및 레벨업을 진행할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Unused components can be decomposed here, which give you Exploration Coins.
talkContent_tw: 多餘元件可在這裡進行分解，可獲得探險幣
talkContent_en: Unused components can be decomposed here, which give you Exploration Coins.
talkContent_kr: 남는 부품은 이곳에서 분해를 진행해 탐험 주화를 획득할 수 있답니다.

talkContent: Adventure Coins can be used to buy components in shops.
talkContent_tw: 探險幣可用作商店購買訓練師需要的元件
talkContent_en: Adventure Coins can be used to buy components in shops.
talkContent_kr: 탐험 주화는 상점에서 트레이너에게 필요한 부품을 구매할 때 사용할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Trainer, please continue your adventure!
talkContent_tw: 訓練師，請繼續冒險吧！
talkContent_en: Trainer, please continue your adventure!
talkContent_kr: "트레이너님, 그럼 모험을 계속하세요!"

talkContent: You may now proceed to #C0xE77421#[Aether Paradise]#C0x5B545B# for treasure hunt!
talkContent_tw: 可以到#C0xE77421#【以太樂園】#C0x5B545B#探索尋寶了哦
talkContent_en: You may now proceed to #C0xE77421#[Aether Paradise]#C0x5B545B# for treasure hunt!
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#[에테르파라다이스]#C0x5B545B#에서 보물찾기를 진행할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the #C0x5B545B# selection interface for #C0xE77421# [Adventure]
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入#C0xE77421#【冒險】#C0x5B545B#的選擇介面
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the #C0x5B545B# selection interface for #C0xE77421# [Adventure]
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 #C0xE77421#[모험]#C0x5B545B# 선택 메뉴로 들어가세요.

talkContent: Tap here to enter #C0xE77421#[Aether Paradise]
talkContent_tw: 從這裡可以點擊進入#C0xE77421#【以太樂園】
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter #C0xE77421#[Aether Paradise]
talkContent_kr: 이곳에서 #C0xE77421#[에테르파라다이스]에 입장할 수 있어요.

talkContent: Welcome to the#C0xE77421#[Aether Paradise]#C0x5B545B#! At the Paradise, you will experience the fun challenges of wisdom and opportunity!
talkContent_tw: 歡迎來到#C0xE77421#【以太樂園】#C0x5B545B#，在這裡你可以體驗智慧與機緣帶來的挑戰的樂趣
talkContent_en: Welcome to the#C0xE77421#[Aether Paradise]#C0x5B545B#! At the Paradise, you will experience the fun challenges of wisdom and opportunity!
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#[에테르파라다이스]#C0x5B545B#에 오신 것을 환영합니다. 이곳에서는 지혜와 인연을 통한 도전의 즐거움을 체험할 수 있답니다.

talkContent: Tap here to begin today's adventure.
talkContent_tw: 點此開始今日的冒險
talkContent_en: Tap here to begin today's adventure.
talkContent_kr: 터치해 오늘의 모험을 시작하세요.

talkContent: There is a total of X floors in the Aether Paradise, each floor has 7-12 rooms, and each room has 1-4 options.
talkContent_tw: 以太樂園共有X層，每層有7-12個房間，每個房間有1-4個選項
talkContent_en: There is a total of X floors in the Aether Paradise, each floor has 7-12 rooms, and each room has 1-4 options.
talkContent_kr: "에테르파라다이스에는 총 X개의 층이 존재합니다. 각 층은 7~12개의 방으로 이루어져 있고, 방마다 1~4개의 선택지가 있답니다."

talkContent: There are options available for each room. Choosing different options can bring different effects and affect your next selection path.
talkContent_tw: 這裡是每個房間可選選項，選擇不同選項可以帶來不同的效果，並影響接下來的路線選擇
talkContent_en: There are options available for each room. Choosing different options can bring different effects and affect your next selection path.
talkContent_kr: "이곳은 각 방의 선택지입니다. 선택지마다 다른 효과가 나타나며, 이어지는 노선의 선택에 영향을 줍니다."

talkContent: This is your progress and current points earning.
talkContent_tw: 這裡是你的進度和當前積分
talkContent_en: This is your progress and current points earning.
talkContent_kr: 이쪽은 현재 진행도와 포인트입니다.

talkContent: You can claim point rewards here after earning a certain number of points.
talkContent_tw: 累積到一定積分後，可以在這裡領取積分獎勵
talkContent_en: You can claim point rewards here after earning a certain number of points.
talkContent_kr: 포인트가 일정 목표에 도달하면 포인트 보상을 수령할 수 있답니다.

talkContent: Well then, you may now begin your performance, I mean, adventure!
talkContent_tw: 那麼，請開始你的表演…...嗯哼……冒險！
talkContent_en: Well then, you may now begin your performance, I mean, adventure!
talkContent_kr: "그럼... 후훗, 이제 모험을 시작하세요!"

talkContent: Dear trainer, Element Challenge is open.
talkContent_tw: 親愛的訓練師，元素挑戰已開啟
talkContent_en: Dear trainer, Element Challenge is open.
talkContent_kr: "트레이너님, 엘리멘탈 챌린지가 개방됐어요."

talkContent: Dear trainer, Element Challenge is open.
talkContent_tw: 親愛的訓練師，元素挑戰已開啟
talkContent_en: Dear trainer, Element Challenge is open.
talkContent_kr: "트레이너님, 엘리멘탈 챌린지가 개방됐어요."

talkContent: You can select one of the elements to challenge in this interface.
talkContent_tw: 可在該介面選擇其中一個元素來進行挑戰
talkContent_en: You can select one of the elements to challenge in this interface.
talkContent_kr: 해당 메뉴에서 엘리먼트를 선택해 도전을 진행하세요.

talkContent: Tap "Pokémon of the Day" to check information overview of the day.
talkContent_tw: 點擊“今日精靈”可檢視今日的總覽資訊
talkContent_en: Tap "Pokémon of the Day" to check information overview of the day.
talkContent_kr: 오늘의 포켓몬을 터치하면 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.

talkContent: Display all elements available for challenge today and the corresponding target Pokémons.
talkContent_tw: 顯示今日所有可挑戰的元素以及對應的目標精靈
talkContent_en: Display all elements available for challenge today and the corresponding target Pokémons.
talkContent_kr: 오늘의 모든 도전 가능한 엘리먼트 및 해당하는 목표 포켓몬이 표시됩니다.

talkContent: Trainers can select the element type levels based on the activated Pokémons displayed.
talkContent_tw: 玩家可根據顯示已啟動的精靈來選擇元素屬性關卡。
talkContent_en: Trainers can select the element type levels based on the activated Pokémons displayed.
talkContent_kr: 트레이너는 활성화된 포켓몬에 따라 엘리먼트 속성의 스테이지를 선택할 수 있습니다.

talkContent: Let's tap on an element and begin the challenge!
talkContent_tw: 讓我們來點擊一個元素進行挑戰吧！
talkContent_en: Let's tap on an element and begin the challenge!
talkContent_kr: 그럼 엘리먼트를 터치해 도전을 진행하세요!

talkContent: Let's go #C0xE77421#【Fishing】#C0x5B545B# now!
talkContent_tw: 可以去#C0xE77421#【釣魚】#C0x5B545B#了哦
talkContent_en: Let's go #C0xE77421#【Fishing】#C0x5B545B# now!
talkContent_kr: 이제 #C0xE77421#[낚시]#C0x5B545B#를 할 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: Tap here to enter #C0xE77421#【Adventure】#C0x5B545B# selection interface
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡進入#C0xE77421#【冒險】#C0x5B545B#的選擇介面
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter #C0xE77421#【Adventure】#C0x5B545B# selection interface
talkContent_kr: 여길 터치해 #C0xE77421#[모험]#C0x5B545B# 선택 메뉴로 들어가세요.

talkContent: Tap here to enter the #C0xE77421#【Fishing】 feature
talkContent_tw: 從這裡可以點擊進入#C0xE77421#【釣魚】
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter the #C0xE77421#【Fishing】 feature
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#[낚시]는 여기에서 입장할 수 있어 로토.

talkContent: Welcome to #C0xE77421#【Fishing】#C0x5B545B#, you can feel the joy of fishing here, and maybe get some rare Pokémons
talkContent_tw: 歡迎來到#C0xE77421#【釣魚】#C0x5B545B#，在這裡你可以感受垂釣的喜悅，說不定還能釣上稀有的精靈哦
talkContent_en: Welcome to #C0xE77421#【Fishing】#C0x5B545B#, you can feel the joy of fishing here, and maybe get some rare Pokémons
talkContent_kr: "#C0xE77421#[낚시]#C0x5B545B# 체험을 시작하신 것을 환영합니다. 이곳에서는 낚시의 즐거움을 체험할 수 있고, 희귀한 포켓몬을 얻을 수도 있답니다."

talkContent: Tap here to enter Fishing interface
talkContent_tw: 點此進入釣魚場景。
talkContent_en: Tap here to enter Fishing interface
talkContent_kr: 터치해 낚시 맵에 입장하세요.

talkContent: Tap here to purchase and switch bait
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡可以購買和切換魚餌
talkContent_en: Tap here to purchase and switch bait
talkContent_kr: 이곳에서 미끼 구매 및 전환이 가능합니다.

talkContent: Tap here to purchase and switch fishing pole
talkContent_tw: 點擊這裡可以購買和切換魚竿
talkContent_en: Tap here to purchase and switch fishing pole
talkContent_kr: 이곳에서는 낚싯대 구매 및 전환이 가능합니다.

talkContent: Can't go fishing without using pole and bait
talkContent_tw: 不使用魚竿和魚餌就無法釣魚哦
talkContent_en: Can't go fishing without using pole and bait
talkContent_kr: 낚싯대와 미끼가 없으면 낚시를 할 수 없습니다.

talkContent: After finish setting up fishing pole and bait, tap here to start fishing
talkContent_tw: 設置完魚竿和魚餌後，可以點擊這裡進行釣魚操作
talkContent_en: After finish setting up fishing pole and bait, tap here to start fishing
talkContent_kr: "낚싯대와 미끼를 설정한 후, 이곳을 터치해 낚시를 진행할 수 있어요."

talkContent: Farewell then
talkContent_tw: 那麼，後會有期
talkContent_en: Farewell then
talkContent_kr: 그럼 다음에 또 만나요.

talkContent: Welcome to #C0xE77421#【Safari Zone】#C0x5B545B#, tap to select route and enter to challenge
talkContent_tw: 歡迎來到#C0xE77421#【狩獵地帶】#C0x5B545B#，點擊選擇線路按鈕可進入該線路進行挑戰
talkContent_en: Welcome to #C0xE77421#【Safari Zone】#C0x5B545B#, tap to select route and enter to challenge
talkContent_kr: #C0xE77421#[사냥 지대]#C0x5B545B#에 오신 것을 환영합니다. 코스 선택 버튼을 클릭하시면 하당하는 코스로 들어가 도전할 수 있습니다.

talkContent: The upper area is the current progress, the small patterns placed here indicate the current and subsequent types of events encountered
talkContent_tw: 上方區域為當前的進度，這裡擺放的小圖案表示當前以及後續遇到的事件類型
talkContent_en: The upper area is the current progress, the small patterns placed here indicate the current and subsequent types of events encountered
talkContent_kr: 위쪽 구역은 현재의 진도이며,  여기 있는 작은 도안은 현재와 다음에 만날 사건 유형을 표시합니다.

talkContent: Current huntting route bonus effect will be displayed here, only effective at this gameplay
talkContent_tw: 這裡顯示本次狩獵線路中獲得的效果加成，僅在本次玩法中生效
talkContent_en: Current huntting route bonus effect will be displayed here, only effective at this gameplay
talkContent_kr: 여기에는 이번 사냥 코스에서 획득한 효과 보너스를 표시하며, 이번에서만 유효합니다.

talkContent: This is the event we encounter, let's start challenge!
talkContent_tw: 這個就是我們遇到的事件啦~讓我們開啟挑戰~
talkContent_en: This is the event we encounter, let's start challenge!
talkContent_kr: 이건 바로 우리가 만난 사건입니다~ 어서 도전해보자~

talkContent: New feature#C0xE77421#[union]#C0x5B545B#  is now open!

talkContent: Applications have to be approved by the management. Certain unions can click to join directly.

talkContent: If you want to find yourself a home quickly, you can tap [Quick Join] to instantly join a union that meets the requirement.

talkContent: If you've not joined a union or have not found a union of your choice, you may tap [Create union] to build your own union.
